public class Assertion
extends Assumption

The Assertion class is a special kind of Assumption that is not retractable. Once the Assertion has been made, the Cryptographer has accepted the Assumption to be true and will no longer allow the KnowledgeSource to interject its thoughts or facts surrounding the assertion's domain.

Assertion - "(def.) a confident or forceful statement of fact or belief"

Version:
1.0.0-RC
